referred_to_by.content: Jeronimus Tonneman [1687-1750], Amsterdam, Netherlands; Maria Tonneman [d. 1752] (by inheritance), Amsterdam, Netherlands; Maria Tonneman sale, Amsterdam, Netherlands (October 21, 1754); Jonkheer Johan Goll van Franckenstein, Sr. [1722-1785], Amsterdam, Netherlands; Jonkheer Johan Goll van Franckenstein, Jr. [1756-1821], Amsterdam, Netherlands; Jonkheer Pieter Hendrick Goll van Franckenstein [1787-1832], Amsterdam, Netherlands; Jonkheer Pieter Hendrick Goll van Franckenstein sale, Amsterdam, Netherlands (July 1, 1833); Cornelis Steffelaar [1797-1861], Amsterdam and Haarlem, Netherlands; (possibly) Cornelis Steffelaar sale, Amsterdam, Netherlands (October 15-16, 1861); Antonius Wilhelmus Marie Mensing [1866-1936] Amsterdam and Aerdenhout, Netherlands; Antonius Wilhelmus Marie Mensing sale, Amsterdam, Netherlands (October 26, 1937); Private Collection, Amsterdam, Netherlands; the Cleveland Museum of Art, Cleveland, OH (March 4, 2019)
